{"tid":1462401,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[必勝] 以眼還眼！","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:25.000Z","uid":282506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d999ceb4d9479ee2c629d8eed5c8d9ec1351beee","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港豬主動恐暴襲擊機場，<br />\n無差別阻撓國際訪港旅客正常登機返屋企，<br />\n無差別奪走人哋返屋企自由嘅權力，<br />\n愛國愛港支持機場特警用MP5清場、支持愛國軍團齊去機場助機場特警執法。<br />\n<br />\n爲免恐怖主義漫延導致香港國際機場癱瘓無法正常運作，<br />\n愛國愛港全力支持根據基本法第18條實施戒嚴，<br />\n然後根據基本法第20條，<br />\n將立法權授予行政長官，<br />\n直接臨時訂立罪犯移交條例，<br />\n送佢哋班恐怖份子去新疆食愛國飯。<br />\n<br />\n以牙還牙，以眼還眼，<br />\n以人奪我自由還以無差別奪走人哋返屋企嘅自由！<br />\n以豬還豬！<br />\n<br />\n完美融入大灣區三線城市！<br />\n紅軍去港國際地位戰略必勝！<br />\n紅軍去港國際地位戰略必勝！<br />\n紅軍去港國際地位戰略必勝！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2b61d903d71d569239a6d97e987c3acd17a8091f","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1119c7c5bf794efe04ea4c557639b8ec14fcd086","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b61d903d71d569239a6d97e987c3acd17a8091f","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd366fcc055cd5415199ece83bb34f749addcc24","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abeca4b937e6ba9c00909bc1fd26129188a52087","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d999ceb4d9479ee2c629d8eed5c8d9ec1351beee","tid":1462401,"uid":282506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,